name: Postal de la taguarita
description:
Inspired by the taguaras of the Chinozolanos who have been a place for friends, families, soccer/baseball games, some fights, and many joys in the middle of Chinese rice with sweet and sour chicken and a couple of beers. Collect your digital postcards and use your stamps, send love to that person who is not physically present but is present in your mind and heart.

SP: Inspirada en las taguaras de los chinozolanos que han sido encuentro de panas, familias, juegos de futbol/beisbol, algunas peleas y muchas alegrias en medio de arroz chino con pollo agridulce y par de cervezas. Colecciona tus postales digitales y usa tus estampillas, envíale amor a esa persona que no está presente físicamente pero sí presente en tu mente y corazón.

✧ You can send this collectible postcard to your significant other, family, and friends.

✧ Concept, Design, and animation by @faintenkiu | imyanez.tez

✧ This collectible postcard is also part of the first Expo of the "La Tokenia-NFTaguara" community. 

✧ Follow the artist at @faintenkiu on Twitter.
